"a.有触觉的 【英】 adj.有触觉的 (relating to the sense of touch) 【考】 tactile : touch / affective : emotion(有触觉的→触觉/有 感情的→感情) 【记】 tact(接触)+ile→触 觉的 【同】 同根词：contact(联 系)；tactometer(触 觉测量器) adj. 可用触觉感知的 = tangible; 触觉引起的 【记】tact(n 触觉), ile－触觉的 【参】contact(n /v 接触; 联系) 【类】tactile: touch = affective[sentient]: emotion有触觉的: 触觉 = 有感情的: 感情 【记】contact ile 病，生理上的触觉；textile 布料需要触觉来判断好坏 【相关】tangent(数学中简写为tan，单位圆中是个切线) 接触的, 切线的 tactile (adj.)  1610s, ""perceptible to touch,"" from French tactile (16c.) and directly from Latin tactilis ""tangible, that may be touched,"" from tactus, past participle of tangere ""to touch"" (see tangent (adj.)). Meaning ""of or pertaining to the sense of touch"" is attested from 1650s. Related: Tactility."
